Butler Beats Virginia Commonwealth 70-62, Returns to NCAA Men's Title Game

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-04-03T00:26:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/butler-beats-virginia-commonwealth-70-62-returns-to-ncaa-men-s-title-game.html
Butler University reached the
national final in men’s college basketball for the second
straight year, defeating Virginia Commonwealth University 70-62
in the first of today’s two semifinals.  The  University of Connecticut  and the University of
Kentucky play later for the second spot in the final, to be
contested April 4 at Reliant Stadium in Houston.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  